WEBVTT

00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:40.580
=Reincarnated Love=

00:00:40.780 --> 00:00:43.700
=Episode 5=

00:00:44.340 --> 00:00:50.620
(Huo Mansion)

00:00:53.640 --> 00:00:54.710
What is this?

00:00:55.390 --> 00:00:56.320
We're returning home.

00:00:56.623 --> 00:00:58.756
I prepared some medicine and tonics
for your parents.

00:01:00.470 --> 00:01:01.310
These two

00:01:01.670 --> 00:01:03.430
are Physician Wu and Nanny Qiu.

00:01:03.750 --> 00:01:05.156
Physician Wu is skilled in medicine.

00:01:05.230 --> 00:01:06.560
Nanny Qiu is meticulous.

00:01:06.950 --> 00:01:08.790
They'll take care
of your parents' daily life.

00:01:10.230 --> 00:01:11.280
The people behind you

00:01:11.840 --> 00:01:14.000
are guards I arranged
to protect their safety.

00:01:18.840 --> 00:01:19.710
How thoughtful of you.

00:01:21.480 --> 00:01:22.320
Mr. Huo.

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:25.840
Mr. Huo.

00:01:26.120 --> 00:01:26.865
Mrs. Huo.

00:01:26.876 --> 00:01:27.932
A summons from the Palace.

00:01:27.943 --> 00:01:28.913
It may be urgent.

00:01:32.380 --> 00:01:33.230
Go now.

00:01:33.230 --> 00:01:34.070
Work come first.

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:37.480
Then,

00:01:38.640 --> 00:01:39.870
please take extra care.

00:01:43.580 --> 00:01:46.220
(Huo Mansion)

00:01:55.180 --> 00:01:57.820
(Jiang Mansion)

00:01:57.840 --> 00:01:58.690
Ruyan,

00:01:58.710 --> 00:01:59.590
deliver these herbs

00:01:59.760 --> 00:02:01.310
to Nanny Liu.

00:02:01.590 --> 00:02:03.270
Have her send them
to my mother every day.

00:02:04.230 --> 00:02:05.250
Yes, milady.

00:02:06.870 --> 00:02:07.710
Everyone else,

00:02:08.150 --> 00:02:09.280
stay outside the courtyard.

00:02:09.520 --> 00:02:10.470
Without my order,

00:02:10.680 --> 00:02:11.960
no one may enter.

00:02:12.470 --> 00:02:13.330
Yes.

00:02:13.400 --> 00:02:14.260
Oh, my.

00:02:14.280 --> 00:02:15.930
How imposing of you.

00:02:17.470 --> 00:02:19.000
But where is Mr. Huo?

00:02:23.630 --> 00:02:26.030
The heir was exhausted last night,

00:02:26.800 --> 00:02:28.360
so I let him stay in the room

00:02:28.360 --> 00:02:29.310
to sleep.

00:02:30.960 --> 00:02:32.840
Or perhaps Mr. Huo doesn't value you

00:02:33.056 --> 00:02:34.696
because you got pregnant
before marriage.

00:02:35.150 --> 00:02:35.990
Maybe he married you

00:02:36.120 --> 00:02:37.960
only because of the child in your belly.

00:02:39.750 --> 00:02:41.710
Instead of worrying about me,

00:02:42.240 --> 00:02:44.000
perhaps you should worry

00:02:44.120 --> 00:02:45.470
about your marriage to Zhang San.

00:02:46.120 --> 00:02:46.960
You...

00:02:47.190 --> 00:02:49.260
Ruoli is now the heir's wife,

00:02:49.400 --> 00:02:50.470
with a noble status.

00:02:50.910 --> 00:02:52.000
Why boss us around

00:02:52.590 --> 00:02:53.960
at your maternal home?

00:02:54.243 --> 00:02:55.789
My father has been ill for a long time.

00:02:56.630 --> 00:02:58.190
Yet the physicians here

00:02:58.190 --> 00:02:59.680
haven't been effective.

00:03:00.520 --> 00:03:02.750
Physician Wu has excellent skills,

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:05.590
so I invited him to check
my father's pulse.

00:03:05.650 --> 00:03:07.376
We knew you came home
to show filial piety,

00:03:07.387 --> 00:03:08.371
but outsiders might think

00:03:08.382 --> 00:03:09.400
you brought the Huo guards

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:10.680
to raid us.

00:03:12.150 --> 00:03:14.430
Those people are only here
to serve my parents.

00:03:15.030 --> 00:03:16.283
They won't touch anything here.

00:03:17.150 --> 00:03:19.360
Yet you and Uncle keep obstructing me.

00:03:20.030 --> 00:03:20.870
Do you fear

00:03:21.080 --> 00:03:22.310
I might discover something

00:03:22.840 --> 00:03:23.800
I shouldn't?

00:03:24.120 --> 00:03:24.960
Insolent thing.

00:03:25.800 --> 00:03:27.630
This is not your place to act wildly.

00:03:28.960 --> 00:03:30.680
Throw all these outsiders out.

00:03:30.840 --> 00:03:31.680
Wait.

00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:39.150
I wonder if you had fun

00:03:39.150 --> 00:03:41.240
at Tipsy House last night?

00:04:18.390 --> 00:04:19.230
You...

00:04:20.430 --> 00:04:22.190
You sent someone to follow me?

00:04:23.920 --> 00:04:24.870
Rest assured, Uncle.

00:04:25.430 --> 00:04:27.870
I'll keep this matter secret.

00:04:28.950 --> 00:04:29.870
After all,

00:04:30.310 --> 00:04:32.270
if such disgraceful behavior

00:04:32.270 --> 00:04:34.120
were to spread,

00:04:34.430 --> 00:04:35.270
it would disgrace

00:04:35.390 --> 00:04:36.750
the family as well.

00:04:37.750 --> 00:04:38.590
Don't you agree?

00:04:40.120 --> 00:04:40.960
Good.

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:43.120
Good.

00:04:44.190 --> 00:04:45.430
In that case,

00:04:45.830 --> 00:04:48.310
do as she says.

00:04:48.870 --> 00:04:49.710
Father.

00:04:50.950 --> 00:04:51.830
Silence.

00:05:10.270 --> 00:05:11.110
Ruyan,

00:05:11.750 --> 00:05:13.510
go see if Father's medicine is ready.

00:05:13.950 --> 00:05:14.910
Yes, milady.

00:05:31.600 --> 00:05:32.440
Wretch.

00:05:33.240 --> 00:05:34.870
I told you to keep an eye
on Jiang Ruoli.

00:05:34.950 --> 00:05:36.600
Is this how you do your job?

00:05:37.560 --> 00:05:38.480
She sent people in.

00:05:39.190 --> 00:05:40.190
Why didn't you report it?

00:05:42.830 --> 00:05:43.670
Master,

00:05:44.430 --> 00:05:45.270
I didn't know.

00:05:47.720 --> 00:05:48.673
It happened so suddenly.

00:05:49.160 --> 00:05:50.620
I had no time to send word.

00:05:52.160 --> 00:05:53.430
I truly know my mistake.

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:56.950
Do you think that I can't deal with you

00:05:58.310 --> 00:06:00.830
now that you're in the Huo Mansion?

00:06:01.630 --> 00:06:02.470
Tell me.

00:06:03.720 --> 00:06:05.510
How should I punish you?

00:06:07.630 --> 00:06:08.600
Master, spare me.

00:06:08.870 --> 00:06:10.390
I truly know my mistake.

00:06:13.390 --> 00:06:14.230
Who told you

00:06:15.430 --> 00:06:18.480
to have such a seductive face?

00:06:19.070 --> 00:06:20.240
I missed you to death

00:06:20.720 --> 00:06:22.240
after not seeing you for so long.

00:06:22.680 --> 00:06:23.520
Master, please don't.

00:06:25.120 --> 00:06:26.750
I already carry your child.

00:06:29.240 --> 00:06:30.160
That is fine.

00:06:30.750 --> 00:06:32.120
Be obedient.

00:06:32.310 --> 00:06:34.920
I'll raise you to be a concubine.

00:06:36.070 --> 00:06:36.910
Master.

00:06:36.960 --> 00:06:37.830
Master.

00:06:37.950 --> 00:06:38.790
Ruyan?

00:06:39.750 --> 00:06:40.590
Ruyan?

00:06:42.160 --> 00:06:43.000
Mrs. Huo is outside.

00:06:43.270 --> 00:06:44.480
She will hear it.

00:06:46.750 --> 00:06:48.510
That makes it more exciting.

00:06:49.270 --> 00:06:50.240
Little wretch.

00:06:51.070 --> 00:06:52.190
Behave yourself.

00:06:52.360 --> 00:06:53.200
Master.

00:06:53.630 --> 00:06:54.470
Master.

00:06:55.680 --> 00:06:56.520
Ruyan?

00:06:58.120 --> 00:06:58.960
Ruyan?

00:07:33.800 --> 00:07:34.640
Milady.

00:07:36.510 --> 00:07:37.350
Ruyan.

00:07:43.560 --> 00:07:45.360
Milady, why are you here?

00:07:45.383 --> 00:07:46.739
I asked you to check the medicine.

00:07:46.750 --> 00:07:47.723
Why did it take so long?

00:07:48.190 --> 00:07:49.360
The medicine is already done.

00:07:49.680 --> 00:07:51.040
I had someone deliver it just now.

00:07:51.680 --> 00:07:53.430
I went to the storeroom
to find some cloth

00:07:53.720 --> 00:07:56.240
to sew soft cushions for your parents.

00:07:56.423 --> 00:07:57.916
They'll make sitting more comfortable.

00:07:59.160 --> 00:08:00.120
I see.

00:08:00.510 --> 00:08:01.390
It's getting late.

00:08:01.390 --> 00:08:02.230
Let's return.

00:08:02.510 --> 00:08:03.350
Yes.

00:08:34.910 --> 00:08:36.200
Dear, be careful.

00:08:36.990 --> 00:08:39.450
♪Gentle rain seeps into the deep night♪

00:08:39.450 --> 00:08:41.710
♪Stirring the jasmine from slumber♪

00:08:44.730 --> 00:08:45.630
No need to trouble you.

00:08:45.630 --> 00:08:48.220
♪Bringing fresh mud for the home♪

00:08:49.490 --> 00:08:51.760
♪Gazing afar at the roadside
that I once knew♪

00:08:51.760 --> 00:08:54.920
♪Lush grass swayed in abundance♪

00:08:55.450 --> 00:08:58.980
♪Though beauty abounds,
it answered not your call♪

00:08:59.510 --> 00:09:00.390
What are you doing?

00:09:00.390 --> 00:09:01.240
Let go of me.

00:09:01.790 --> 00:09:02.630
Let go.

00:09:04.200 --> 00:09:05.240
You're pregnant.

00:09:05.790 --> 00:09:06.870
What if you fall?

00:09:08.080 --> 00:09:09.550
I'll carry you inside.

00:09:10.270 --> 00:09:11.270
That would be the safest.

00:09:12.860 --> 00:09:14.480
♪That same gentle smile♪

00:09:14.480 --> 00:09:19.030
♪Each hides a trace of familiarity♪

00:09:19.380 --> 00:09:21.430
♪Let passions pour freely♪

00:09:21.430 --> 00:09:24.170
♪How much do you truly know♪

00:09:24.540 --> 00:09:27.210
♪I gift you a sprig of jasmine♪

00:09:27.210 --> 00:09:30.660
♪May we never part,
bound from dawn to dusk♪

00:09:30.660 --> 00:09:33.310
♪Who'd think parting comes so easily♪

00:09:33.310 --> 00:09:36.820
♪Yet reunion hardly comes by♪

00:09:36.820 --> 00:09:39.500
♪You always cheer me up♪

00:09:39.500 --> 00:09:43.830
♪That year's urgent meeting
in a city of drifting petals♪

00:09:44.130 --> 00:09:49.670
♪Falling into dreams,
this feeling lingers♪

00:09:51.810 --> 00:09:52.670
Father,

00:09:52.790 --> 00:09:54.910
I stewed this bird's nest soup.

00:09:55.150 --> 00:09:56.510
It simmered for four hours.

00:09:56.910 --> 00:09:57.923
It can nourish the lungs.

00:10:00.120 --> 00:10:00.960
Food?

00:10:01.440 --> 00:10:02.790
You still think about food?

00:10:03.440 --> 00:10:04.960
Look at Jiang Ruoli.

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:06.960
Before, her father was the Chancellor

00:10:07.200 --> 00:10:08.200
and suppressed you.

00:10:09.240 --> 00:10:11.120
Now, her father is a living corpse.

00:10:11.720 --> 00:10:13.150
She's just an orphan without support,

00:10:13.550 --> 00:10:15.600
yet she managed
to marry the Duke's heir.

00:10:16.720 --> 00:10:17.670
But you?

00:10:18.550 --> 00:10:19.480
I spent so much effort

00:10:20.750 --> 00:10:21.750
raising you

00:10:21.750 --> 00:10:23.510
into a noble lady in the capital.

00:10:24.390 --> 00:10:25.320
And what happened?

00:10:26.270 --> 00:10:28.390
You are not even as good as her!

00:10:28.870 --> 00:10:29.803
Please calm your anger.

00:10:30.910 --> 00:10:32.270
Useless trash.

00:10:38.790 --> 00:10:39.630
That woman!

00:10:40.510 --> 00:10:42.080
Relying on Huo Linchuan,

00:10:42.390 --> 00:10:43.670
she's become so arrogant.

00:10:44.380 --> 00:10:45.230
Milady.

00:10:45.240 --> 00:10:46.320
Milady, please calm down.

00:10:47.870 --> 00:10:48.870
Jiang Ruoli,

00:10:49.750 --> 00:10:51.870
I'll make you climb higher

00:10:52.600 --> 00:10:54.150
only to fall harder.

00:10:56.670 --> 00:10:58.036
I've interrogated the men in black

00:10:58.510 --> 00:10:59.550
from the Lantern Festival.

00:11:00.200 --> 00:11:01.440
They were mercenaries.

00:11:02.600 --> 00:11:03.440
Who was the employer?

00:11:04.750 --> 00:11:06.130
The employer changed several times.

00:11:07.150 --> 00:11:08.483
The real culprit is still unknown.

00:11:10.790 --> 00:11:12.223
As long as the culprit is not found,

00:11:12.870 --> 00:11:15.150
my family will never know peace.

00:11:16.510 --> 00:11:17.350
Don't worry.

00:11:19.120 --> 00:11:19.960
I will

00:11:20.750 --> 00:11:21.960
keep investigating this

00:11:23.510 --> 00:11:25.030
until the real culprit is found.

00:11:35.630 --> 00:11:36.470
Dear,

00:11:38.000 --> 00:11:39.200
have you had any dreams lately?

00:11:51.890 --> 00:11:53.240
Since I married you,

00:11:53.790 --> 00:11:55.120
the food has been delicious,

00:11:55.503 --> 00:11:56.916
the servants attentive in every way,

00:11:57.390 --> 00:11:58.360
and my sleep peaceful.

00:11:59.000 --> 00:11:59.840
I haven't dreamed.

00:12:05.000 --> 00:12:05.840
That is

00:12:07.670 --> 00:12:08.510
very good.

00:12:11.870 --> 00:12:13.160
Mr. and Mrs. Huo.

00:12:14.150 --> 00:12:15.680
Lady Wanyue has sent an invitation

00:12:16.030 --> 00:12:18.150
(Invitation)
for a tea gathering tomorrow.

00:12:22.580 --> 00:12:26.980
(Jiang Mansion)

00:12:31.960 --> 00:12:32.800
Everyone,

00:12:33.000 --> 00:12:35.150
these are Jade Dew Cakes
I had the kitchen make.

00:12:35.480 --> 00:12:37.800
They are made
with osmanthus petals from this morning.

00:12:37.910 --> 00:12:39.170
Especially sweet and delicious.

00:12:39.270 --> 00:12:40.600
I invited you all to taste them.

00:12:41.270 --> 00:12:42.720
- How thoughtful.
- How thoughtful.

00:12:54.750 --> 00:12:56.630
Ruoli, you're with child.

00:12:56.720 --> 00:12:59.240
Greasy food must be hard for you to eat.

00:12:59.670 --> 00:13:01.580
These cakes are very appetizing.

00:13:01.840 --> 00:13:02.960
Please try them.

00:13:05.120 --> 00:13:06.750
(Jiang Wanyue,)

00:13:07.510 --> 00:13:09.720
(you truly are my good cousin.)

00:13:12.390 --> 00:13:13.600
Thanks for your effort.

00:13:14.630 --> 00:13:15.480
These cakes

00:13:15.870 --> 00:13:17.600
look absolutely tempting.

00:13:18.320 --> 00:13:20.120
Then I'll accept your kindness.

00:13:38.270 --> 00:13:39.670
Indeed, sweet and delicious.

00:13:44.630 --> 00:13:45.480
(Jiang Ruoli,)

00:13:45.870 --> 00:13:48.510
(let me see how you'll stay arrogant)

00:13:48.870 --> 00:13:50.270
(without the child.)

00:14:00.360 --> 00:14:01.200
Milady.

00:14:01.910 --> 00:14:02.760
My stomach.

00:14:02.790 --> 00:14:04.080
- Milady.
- Ah.

00:14:04.510 --> 00:14:05.540
- Ah.
- Milady.

00:14:06.600 --> 00:14:07.653
- What happened?
- Milady.

00:14:07.750 --> 00:14:08.590
It hurts so much.

00:14:09.240 --> 00:14:10.080
Milady.

00:14:10.840 --> 00:14:11.870
My child.

00:14:12.550 --> 00:14:13.390
My child.

00:14:13.390 --> 00:14:14.230
(Dear cousin,)

00:14:15.000 --> 00:14:16.600
(since I'm putting on a show for you,)

00:14:17.000 --> 00:14:18.510
- (it must look real.)
- Milady.

00:14:18.510 --> 00:14:19.350
My child.

00:14:20.240 --> 00:14:21.080
Milady, this...

00:14:23.200 --> 00:14:24.040
Milady.

00:14:24.350 --> 00:14:25.200
My child.

00:14:25.200 --> 00:14:26.040
Milady.

00:14:28.150 --> 00:14:28.990
Ah.

00:14:29.150 --> 00:14:30.200
My child.

00:14:31.790 --> 00:14:32.756
Master Huaikang is here.

00:14:35.480 --> 00:14:36.320
Father.

00:14:42.720 --> 00:14:43.560
You wretch.

00:14:44.030 --> 00:14:44.870
What have you done?

00:14:45.270 --> 00:14:46.360
Father, I...

00:14:46.360 --> 00:14:48.040
I only wanted to help you
vent your anger.

00:14:49.120 --> 00:14:50.200
You fool.

00:14:50.840 --> 00:14:52.080
Uncle,

00:14:52.840 --> 00:14:54.150
how cruel you are.

00:14:56.840 --> 00:14:57.680
My child...

00:15:00.790 --> 00:15:01.790
Who did this?

00:15:26.640 --> 00:15:28.160
♪The dream shattered♪

00:15:28.520 --> 00:15:30.200
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

00:15:30.200 --> 00:15:31.840
♪Like a restless soul♪

00:15:32.720 --> 00:15:34.280
♪How vague♪

00:15:34.680 --> 00:15:36.200
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

00:15:36.200 --> 00:15:38.440
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

00:15:39.240 --> 00:15:41.840
♪Love and hate entwined♪

00:15:42.320 --> 00:15:45.160
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

00:15:45.800 --> 00:15:50.560
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

00:15:51.160 --> 00:15:52.680
♪When fate falls apart♪

00:15:53.080 --> 00:15:56.640
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

00:15:57.360 --> 00:15:58.920
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

00:15:59.320 --> 00:16:03.040
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

00:16:03.760 --> 00:16:06.600
♪Life after life♪

00:16:07.080 --> 00:16:09.760
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

00:16:10.400 --> 00:16:14.480
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

00:16:14.560 --> 00:16:17.600
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

00:16:17.760 --> 00:16:19.160
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

00:16:19.160 --> 00:16:22.280
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

00:16:22.360 --> 00:16:23.800
♪Now shatter apart♪

00:16:23.920 --> 00:16:27.680
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

00:16:28.400 --> 00:16:31.200
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

00:16:31.480 --> 00:16:34.320
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

00:16:34.640 --> 00:16:39.040
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

00:16:39.280 --> 00:16:42.200
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

00:16:42.320 --> 00:16:46.760
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

00:16:46.960 --> 00:16:52.680
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

00:16:53.120 --> 00:16:55.840
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

00:16:56.080 --> 00:16:58.800
♪Sober or indulge♪

00:16:59.240 --> 00:17:05.240
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪